{
  "stem": "7873.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He, he was a [NON-ENGLISH], read the Torah every Saturday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how I grew up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did that, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I read the Torah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew how to do everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And then--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, not as curly, the, the way they have them here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just to-- the barber had to leave me some, not to touch it, just even them up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And that's how life was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we have friends, a lot of Christian friends-- as a matter of fact, mostly Christian friends.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They spoke our language, the, the, the boys-- the Christian friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This one time, a friend of mine beat up one of the Christian friends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Christian friend went to the rabbi-- to the teacher-- to, to claim that so-and-so beat me up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he says to the Christian guy, he says, what cheder are you going to?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, I don't go to any cheder.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm-- [NON-ENGLISH] was his name, Stanley, like.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, then you're a shegetz?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, yes, I am a shegetz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's how we lived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We grew up with each other till the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they changed their mind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, but everything was supposed to be in a joke, where they make fun of a Jew or anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't so sharp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't so that you would feel bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, we never made fun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, no, the Polish people are very fanatic, very fanatic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you had anything, sometimes they would say so-and-so-- you'll excuse me, but I want to say that-- they urinated near a cross.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See, down there in Poland every few miles, you have a cross, you know, with the blessed mother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you-- there, you salute.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
